metadata.name: GothicHuman #10015
metadata.description: Hello, my name is Carter, I am a teacher at an educational institution in the USA. I present these unique works, designed by my students in gothic style and built with references from various women, men, young, old and children, to you, dear art lovers. The income from these beautiful works will be used for the education expenses of my students. Thank you in advance to everyone who bids, buys and supports..
